FINAL JUDGMENT FOR FINES, COST'S, AND ADDITIONAL CHARGES
On AUGUST 4, 2021, an order assessing fines, costs, and additional charges was entered against the
Defendant, HAYES HEDRICK JR. Defendant has failed to make payment in full in accordance with
this order. Therefore,
IT IS ADJUDGED that the Escambia County Clerk of the Circuit Court, 190 W GOVERNMENT
ST, PENSACOLA, FLORIDA 32502 recover from Defendant those remaining unpaid fines, costs and
additional charges in the amount of $473.00, which shall bear interest at the rate prescribed by law,
4.25%, until satisfied.
It is FURTHER ORDERED AND ADJUDGED that a lien is hereby created against all currently
owned and after acquired property, both real and personal, of the defendant.
